{"tid":426403,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好迷惘唔知想做咩工(求教)","createTime":"2017-10-06T14:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T15:58:35.000Z","uid":102875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"23d9ca42f64b74c6ccbdbe033e12a7bb7c603a61","tid":426403,"uid":102875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"小弟係17年fg 三大垃圾社科<br />\n依家做緊一間算有名嘅NGO PA啦<br />\n點知間野都好鬼死多野做 勁多野要學好似咩system <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又要面對勁多義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完全唔知自己點面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但平時朋友 親戚都覺得我係好多嘢講嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身想讀社工master 但都要面對好多義工但係我返咗工之後我發覺自己唔係咁鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我真係唔知自己想做咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但錢對於我來講真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟點先知道自己啱做咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同有咩工會請fg 垃圾社科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9d68230830a1515b4fdcd7e7d712b50034d80d","tid":426403,"uid":12536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"非三大社科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fb1e9ae43cc50441c1d388bd4c4ef84b47ac0a","tid":426403,"uid":140696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"pa咪好少人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48c49f674b3a89b4d5eeb748f072486c2e6ca93","tid":426403,"uid":140696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"非三大社科 fg<br />\n下星期番pw"},{"pid":"c16965baffccd311eb1b6f6bf314b7219e6b6680","tid":426403,"uid":102875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep